xrow Sass is a clone of eZJscorePacker template operator

Use these functions according to eZJscore extension:
- xrowsass
- xrowsass_require
- xrowsass_load
- xrowsassfiles

Used Compiler
https://github.com/richthegeek/phpsass
A compiler for SASS/SCSS written in PHP, brought up to date (approx 3.2) from a fork of PHamlP: http://code.google.com/p/phamlp/

optional
The packer generates a copy of the packed file which has a static filename
This could be useful for providing the css-file for external services.
path: example.com/var/cache/public/<siteaccess_name>_packed.css